It is possible for someone to have cancer without symptoms, to not tell anyone until the very end, to die suddenly... but it's very unlikely, particularly when it also happens to be half of a couple that secretly played a character in classic &quot;mangina&quot; fashion.  And this is coming from someone who has crossed the gender barrier online before.  I know what it's like.  I also know the stories others will resort to to cover their tracks when things get out of hand.<br>
